All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable, ECUMonitor
public class SSMOBD2Monitor
extends RS232Monitor

This extension to the SSMMonitor is setup to use the OBD-II version of SSM * http://scoobypedia.co.uk/index.php/Knowledge/ReadingAndReflashingECUs http://www.scoobypedia.co.uk/index.php/Knowledge/ECUVersionCompatibilityList#toc3 http://www.enginuity.org/search.php?search_id=1844875639&start=105 http://www.vwrx.com/index.php?pg=selectmonitor
